<h3>DiscoSense: Commonsense Reasoning with Discourse Connectives</h3>
Prajjwal Bhargava and Vincent Ng.
<br>
<i>Proceedings of the 2022 Conference on Empirical Methods in Natural Language Processing</i>, 2022. 


<p>Click here for the 
